payload.doc:
The incoming webhook body or the ProseMirror JSON document to convert. Accepts three formats:

1. The full Hocuspocus webhook body — the action will auto-extract the document from payload.document
2. A document object with named fields — e.g. { "default": { "type": "doc", ... } }
3. Raw ProseMirror JSON — e.g. { "type": "doc", "content": [...] }

In a Bubble workflow triggered by an incoming webhook, use "Request Data's body" to pass the full body.
